                    "algorithm": "sha256",
                    "hashValue": "a3f8c2e1d4b7a9f0e2c5d8b1f4a7c0e3d6b9f2a5c8e1d4b7a0f3c6e9d2b5a8f1"
                }
            ],
            "comment": "SPDX 3.0 NOTE: 'dataset_datasetSize' (52428800 bytes, ~50 MB) and 'dataset_intendedUse' are DEPRECATED in SPDX 3.1 - use 'software_artifactSize' and Core 'intendedUse' instead. Compare with spdx3.1/example07.spdx3.json-draft."
        },
